# Doppler / managed-secrets backend (startd8.secrets): never commit service tokens or local
# secret dumps. Tokens belong in $HOME (~/.startd8/config.json, ~/.doppler) or env — not the repo.
# (doppler.yaml — the non-secret project config — is intentionally NOT ignored.)
*.token
*.tokens
secrets.json
.env.*
!.env.example

